                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On May 1, 1950, Secretary of State Acheson discussed the world situation in
                    executive session before the Senate Foreign Relations Committee; for the record
                    of his testimony, see <hi rend="italic">Reviews of the World Situation,
                        1949–1950: Hearings Held in Executive Session Before the Committee on
                        Foreign Relations, United States Senate</hi> (81st Cong., 1st and 2nd
                    sessions), pages 285–312.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
